{"tid":21734,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"胡國興願重新審視單程證制度","createTime":"2016-12-04T04:44:12.000Z","updateTime":"2016-12-04T07:51:21.000Z","uid":13663,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"c3f36d35a56c29bca17f02b057eb33d895de3fc6","tid":21734,"uid":13663,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-04T04:44:12.000Z","msg":"胡國興願重新審視單程證制度<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://now.com\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fnow.com&d=byei43Pfdy9TlHy68xWwXQT5PszEexF2%2B6H4LydsHP4%3D&h=5403e551\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">now.com</a> 新聞<br />\n27 分鐘前<br />\n【Now新聞台】選委會選舉下星期日舉行，獲選的選委將負責選出新特首。已表態參選的退休法官胡國興，希望其他有意做特首的人快些表態。他表示自己明白市民對社會的不滿，例如單程證制度，他同意有檢視空間。<br />\n今屆學界劍擊比賽，喇沙書院是爭標隊伍之一。曾經入選港隊的胡秉憲，是校隊的總教練，亦是財政司司長曾俊華的劍擊學生。<br />\n<br />\n曾俊華這天都前來為徒弟打氣，回答有關特首選舉的提問時，他同樣穩陣。<br />\n直至日前，曾俊華才稍為鬆了口風，表明會積極考慮會否參選特首。<br />\n上屆特首選舉，梁振英及唐英年都在九月開始準備，十一月正式宣布參選。<br />\n而今屆直至現時為主，退休法官胡國興成為最高調的參選人。<br />\n這一天，他到一間社企在中環經營的臨時外賣店買飯盒。<br />\n胡國興認為自己並不「離地」，亦了解社會的矛盾，知道有市民不滿單程證審批制度。<br />\n胡國興又相信重啟政改能消除目前的社會矛盾。<br />\n今晚播出的時事專題節目經緯線，胡國興會講述更多理念，亦會找來各方人士，點評多名特首熱門人選。"},{"pid":"ae05acc19e8fba6380f1ace5e43c8d9e6c1afe40","tid":21734,"uid":13663,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-04T04:52:08.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"http://i1.kym-cdn.com/entries/icons/original/000/000/142/feelsgood.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fi1.kym-cdn.com%2Fentries%2Ficons%2Foriginal%2F000%2F000%2F142%2Ffeelsgood.jpg&h=772584d5&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"94fe81c7106c3bfc8fee02e0a07d0015b9711c4c","tid":21734,"uid":48157,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-04T04:54:17.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"5670ee863f0122e777deddae930159d91971159b","tid":21734,"uid":29314,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-04T04:56:41.000Z","msg":"然後人大釋法。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n單程證政策屬國防事務，港豬無權干涉。<br />\n<br />\n同日，習近平宣布單程證配額加大十倍。"},{"pid":"d70b4e144763b66df034341b64618b5066832a56","tid":21734,"uid":47659,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-04T05:10:48.000Z","msg":"講得六四唔應該使用武力仲想入閘?<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />唉rip 想入閘就要扮住無良心先呀嘛"},{"pid":"ca6763c6498331e33164bea498165b46790253cd","tid":21734,"uid":13663,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-04T05:14:53.000Z","msg":"😍"},{"pid":"061cbbc3f2440ff6256a256b91f5648e74acf352","tid":21734,"uid":22736,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-04T05:15:52.000Z","msg":"你入到閘先算啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/z.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7c5634d3202ceb0b301ae1b07b437197d6919ea5","tid":21734,"uid":35790,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-04T05:19:59.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>然後人大釋法。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n單程證政策屬國防事務，港豬無權干涉。<br />\n<br />\n同日，習近平宣布單程證配額加大十倍。</blockquote><br />\n釋法後官判DQ港深關卡<br />\n港深一體化<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f56e5e59313bac90949110a785cef4bce6d1d2c7","tid":21734,"uid":34771,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-04T05:28:51.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>然後人大釋法。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n單程證政策屬國防事務，港豬無權干涉。<br />\n<br />\n同日，習近平宣布單程證配額加大十倍。</blockquote><br />\n真 港獨之父？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ef454dc051f4984171a52b3ddc681a52cca67d81","tid":21734,"uid":13663,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-04T06:37:12.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"81a01871fbf317a0e43a3d37ed888859f0f127e0","tid":21734,"uid":50182,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-04T06:40:48.000Z","msg":"選前先講人話 比你選到你夠撚薑執行咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/z.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d912edcc9e7716b80da0647ec5b2e62d2bb156b9","tid":21734,"uid":13663,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"20